snippet.title: Molar Maul - ZX Spectrum Gameplay (Steam Re-Release)
snippet.description:
Originally released in 1983, this unique and bizarre game saw players fight a new and sinister force: a form of mouth bacteria called Dentorium Kamikazium (DK).

In Molar Maul, you move your toothbrush in front of the Imagico toothpaste tube to receive a squirt of toothpaste (containing the only known substance that can combat the DKs: the recently developed chemical compound DKX 11). Move to a tooth and scrub to clean it and repel the DKs, which are unrelenting in their attacks!

Footage from the Steam re-release by Pixel Games UK
